    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2008 BMW M3 (E92) powered by the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8. This engine features individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering exceptional volumetric efficiency. Key preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing. The chassis utilizes a variable M-differential lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing precise lateral dynamics. While the paint and interior show minor signs of spirited use, the drivetrain remains tight with no VANOS noise or subframe issues. A high-performance driver's car with documented service history.",
