    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2015 Audi S5 Coupe in Moonlight Blue Metallic. This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and luxury. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like finish, with only minor, expected peppering on the front bumper from highway commuting. The factory 19-inch wheels are wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport tires with plenty of life left. Inside, the Black Fine Nappa leather seats show very minimal wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster and remain soft and supple. All interior electronics, including the MMI Navigation plus and the premium Bang & Olufsen sound system, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this S5 is top-tier; the 3.0T supercharged engine pulls hard and smooth, and the 7-speed dual-clutch transmission provides crisp, immediate shifts. I have kept a detailed log of all maintenance, including recent DSG fluid service and oil changes every 5,000 miles. It has a clean title and has never been involved in an accident. This is a turn-key car that needs nothing but a new driver.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
